-custom-race-plus-bottle-cage-232727.html\" target=\"_blank\">Buy now from Merlin from £7.50</a></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Specialized Road Inner Tube: RRP £7 – <a href=\"https://tidd.ly/3vyxRZg\" target=\"_blank\">Buy now from Cyclestore for £3.50</a></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bialetti Moka Express Coffee Maker: RRP £29.99 – <a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Bialetti-Express-Espresso-Maker-Silver/dp/B0019M4H16?hvadid=80401845130248&amp;hvnetw=o&amp;hvqmt=e&amp;hvbmt=be&amp;hvdev=c&amp;hvlocint=&amp;hvlocphy=&amp;hvtargid=pla-4584001419426939&amp;th=1&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=cyclist0a-21&amp;linkId=fb093c015a3eaa66c50baea8696c74fe&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\">Buy now from Amazon for £22</a></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Garmin Varia RTL515: RRP £170– <a href=\"https://tidd.ly/4b0hy7J\" target=\"_blank\">Buy now from Tredz for £130</a></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Dhb R2.0 helmet: RRP £50 – <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=1857&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=cyclist+black+friday+wiggle+dhb+helmet&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiggle.com%2Fp%2Fdhb-r2-0-road-helmet\" target=\"_blank\">Buy now from Wiggle for £5</a></strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h2>The best cycling deals as picked by the team at <em>Cyclist</em></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>Giant Contend 2 road bike</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"644\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/Giant-Contend-2-970x644.jpg\" alt=\"Giant Contend 2\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/Giant-Contend-2-970x644.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/Giant-Contend-2-300x199.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/Giant-Contend-2-768x510.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/Giant-Contend-2-750x498.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/Giant-Contend-2-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/Giant-Contend-2-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/Giant-Contend-2-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/Giant-Contend-2.jpg 1133w\" /><figcaption>Giant</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£659 (RRP £879) | <a href=\"https://tidd.ly/3S05St3\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Quality entry-level aluminium road bike with carbon fork</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Eight-speed Shimano groupset</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re after a good quality beginner’s bike or maybe a winter road bike to which you can fit mudguards for wet road duties, the Giant Contend offers great value. Cyclestore is also selling the <a href=\"https://tidd.ly/41Z7NTn\" target=\"_blank\">Giant Liv Avail 2</a> women’s bike for the same price, or you could go for the 9-speed Sora-equipped <a href=\"https://tidd.ly/3SlEkja\" target=\"_blank\">Contend 1</a>, priced at £749, if you would like an upgrade.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from</strong><a href=\"https://tidd.ly/3S05St3\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Cyclestore (£659)</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Endura Pro SL HC Windproof Cycling Jacket II</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"645\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-970x645.jpg\" alt=\"Endura Pro SL HC Windproof Cycling Jacket II\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-300x199.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-768x510.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-1536x1021.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-2048x1361.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-750x498.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-1140x758.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Endura-jacket-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>£49.99 (RRP £139.99) | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=6821&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;campaign=Deals+page&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tredz.co.uk%2F.Endura-Pro-SL-HC-Windproof-Cycling-Jacket-II_238630.htm\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Bold pattern with reflectives for enhanced road presence</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Thermal insulation for comfort in cold, dry conditions</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The Endura Pro SL HC Windproof Cycling Jacket II adds a little more insulation for colder weather riding, but still has the same windproof/water resistant features. The back panel helps wick away moisture to ensure that you stay comfortable.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The bright pattern, which is continued onto the upper back, should help you to increase your road presence and is paired with in-built reflectives for low light riding. </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=6821&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;campaign=Deals+page&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tredz.co.uk%2F.Endura-Pro-SL-HC-Windproof-Cycling-Jacket-II_238630.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Tredz for £49.99</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Castelli Fondo 2 Long Sleeve Jersey</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"650\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Castelli-Fondo-2-970x650.jpg\" alt=\"Castelli Fondo 2 pack shot\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Castelli-Fondo-2-970x650.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Castelli-Fondo-2-300x201.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Castelli-Fondo-2-768x514.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Castelli-Fondo-2-750x502.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Castelli-Fondo-2-1140x764.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Castelli-Fondo-2.jpg 1148w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>£55 (RRP £110) | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=6821&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;campaign=Deals+page&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tredz.co.uk%2F.Castelli-Fondo-2-Long-Sleeve-Cycling-Jersey_242020.htm\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Quoted temperature range from 12-18°C</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Room to layer up for cooler rides</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Castelli reckons that on its own the Fondo 2 jersey is good for temperatures from 12° to 18°C. Add a shell over it and you can go a lot lower. It quotes a weight of 255g for a size medium, so it’s not too heavy either.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Castelli describes the cut as a neutral fit, so it shouldn’t be pro-level tight and should allow you to layer up underneath. There’s a reasonable range of size/colour options on offer at Tredz.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=6821&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;campaign=Deals+page&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tredz.co.uk%2F.Castelli-Fondo-2-Long-Sleeve-Cycling-Jersey_242020.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Tredz for £55</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Castelli Alpha ROS 2 jacket</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"639\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99