one grippers on the palms, for a secure hold on the bars, whatever the weather and the long cuff prevents cold air getting to your wrists or arms. Reflectives on the sides add visibility.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://tidd.ly/48TXsdE\" target=\"_blank\">Le Col for £40</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Elite Custom Race Plus Bottle Cage</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"648\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Elite-Custom-Race-Plus-bottle-cage-970x648.jpg\" alt=\"Elite Custom Race Plus bottle cage\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Elite-Custom-Race-Plus-bottle-cage-970x648.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Elite-Custom-Race-Plus-bottle-cage-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Elite-Custom-Race-Plus-bottle-cage-768x513.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Elite-Custom-Race-Plus-bottle-cage-750x501.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Elite-Custom-Race-Plus-bottle-cage-1140x761.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Elite-Custom-Race-Plus-bottle-cage-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Elite-Custom-Race-Plus-bottle-cage-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Elite-Custom-Race-Plus-bottle-cage-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/04/Elite-Custom-Race-Plus-bottle-cage.jpg 1423w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>£7.50 (RRP £13.99) | <a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=205647X1684865&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.merlincycles.com%2Felite-custom-race-plus-bottle-cage-232727.html\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<u